data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER. This property came on the market ready to live in, you can make SHORT RENT, LONG RENT or simply enjoy it with your family. This charming pool, 6 bedroom property is located on a coveted corner lot within a desirable golf community, probably the LARGEST HOME in Southern Dunes! The great room is designed to fully embrace the Florida lifestyle; The open-plan, double-height design provides a light and airy feel and leads directly through the sliding glass doors to your own private pool terrace! The heated pool also has a spa, garden furniture is included in the transaction. The house has two (2) master bedrooms; The first is located on the ground floor and both the bedroom and the bathroom are fully accessible without steps or stairs. The bathroom features dual sinks, a separate toilet, a garden tub, and a separate shower stall for added privacy and spaciousness. Plenty of space to relax in this open, flexible floor plan. The family room is truly the center of this beautiful home and benefits from cathedral ceilings with access to the kitchen and pool area. The beautiful, bright kitchen has been updated with stainless steel appliances, as has your laundry room. There is a more formal dining room to one side of the kitchen and a breakfast area overlooking the pool. The second Master is located upstairs and also has its own private bathroom. On the second level there are four further good sized bedrooms and two bathrooms separated by a landing, so there is plenty of space for a large family or perfect for holidays. The property's garage has been converted into a games room as an added feature if you wish to rent the house out or use it as a gym/play area, but can also be cleared out to create a spacious two-car room or storage room. You can spend the afternoon floating in the heated pool, the evenings entertaining in the barbecue area, or simply enjoying your own private oasis. Southern Dunes is not only home to a highly rated golf course, but also a beautiful and safe gated community. Dunes community features community pools, a clubhouse, tennis courts, fitness center, and a play area. This is a gated community with 24 hours security. Just a short drive of restaurants, movie theaters, medical centers, well-known stores such as: Winn Dixie, Walmart and Publix. Just 20 minutes from DISNEY. This property is offered fully furnished/turnkey, water purification system throughout the property, TESLA battery valued at over $25,000.00, SOLAR PANELS to be paid at closing, all appliances are brand new. Easy trip to Orlando or Tampa if needed. This home won't last long, so make an appointment to see it today! Under support offers that accept contracts.    https://youtu.be/ci9mBpuA9Ck
